{"type":null,"faqId":14592,"title":"如何升级手机？","answer":"<p>\n<div style=\"border:none;border-top:solid windowtext 1.5pt;\npadding:4.0pt 0cm 0cm 0cm;margin-left:42.55pt;margin-right:0cm\">\n<p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:42.55pt;line-height:12.0pt;page-break-after:avoid;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;border:none;padding:0cm;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Book Antiqua','serif';margin-left:0cm\"><span><br>\n<img width=\"90\" height=\"42\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20140828170941307001.gif\"></span></p>\n</div>\n<div style=\"border:none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.5pt;\npadding:0cm 0cm 4.0pt 0cm;margin-left:42.55pt;margin-right:0cm\">\n<p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:42.55pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;border:none;padding:0cm;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';margin-left:0cm\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\n\">为防止手机内存中的用户数据（如：联系人、信息、通话记录等）在升级时被删除，建议升级前备份手机数据。</span></p>\n</div>\n<p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:56.75pt;text-indent:-14.2pt;line-height:12.0pt;tab-stops:list 42.55pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"><span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;\nfont-family:Wingdings;position:relative;top:-1.0pt;\"><span>l<span style=\"font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在线升级：在线升级前，请连接移动网络或</span><span> WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">网络。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:2.0cm;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\n\">进入<b>设置</b>界面，点击<b>手机升级</b></span><span> &gt; </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">系统软件更新</span><span> &gt; </span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在线升级</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，根据屏幕提示完成升级。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:42.55pt;line-height:12.0pt;page-break-after:avoid;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"><span><img width=\"558\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20140828170941225002.gif\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:42.55pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:56.75pt;text-indent:-14.2pt;line-height:12.0pt;tab-stops:list 42.55pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"><span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;\nfont-family:Wingdings;position:relative;top:-1.0pt;\"><span>l<span style=\"font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">本地升级：进入</span> <span><a href=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/cn/\" title=\" \">http://consumer.huawei.com/cn/</a>\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\n\">下载软件升级包，插入</span><span>\nmicroSD </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\n\">卡，并将升级包中的</span><span> download\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\n\">文件夹放入</span><span> microSD </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">卡根目录下。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:2.0cm;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\n\">然后进入<b>设置</b>界面，点击<b>手机升级</b></span> <span>&gt; </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">系统软件更新</span> </b><span>&gt; </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">本地升级</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，根据屏幕提示完成升级。您也可以参考下载的软件升级包中的升级指导。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:42.55pt;line-height:12.0pt;page-break-after:avoid;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"><span><img border=\"0\" width=\"558\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20140828170941777003.gif\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:42.55pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:42.55pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"><span>* </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\n\">图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准。</span></p>\n<br>\n</p>","faqTypeId":141,"faqType":"备份恢复与升级","useful":4,"unUseful":17,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"6653","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Backup-Restore-Update","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1409216998000,"seriesProductName":"Holly-T00,Holly-U10","visitedTimes":2991,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"2","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}